snippet.title: Memories of a Hedgehog - Game - Demo 0.6 - Trailer English
snippet.description:
Hello people, today I bring you the following Demo of my game, this time it is just an update with some bugs corrected, some improvements in the level and most relevant, multilanguage, I worked in what is the selection of which language you want To see The game at the beginning, for what more people can play it without problems, I still consider this demo as Incomplete, since it is not yet Demo 1.0, but still, I hope you like the slight changes.

Download:  https://mega.nz/#!RoYg0Bbb!K-wF5q1zPUwDxLq3ZyO2jkxAJtvTd2pqIf4Y7c3dLyg

If you like, give in Like, and you want see more, subscribe, also, follow me in Facebook Page and see my Pictures in Deviant Art, if you want, can share the video in your Facebook.

Facebook's Page: https://www.facebook.com/JapoloyPaletin.JyP.Productions
